* 1955 – &quot;Jagiellonia Białystok Budowlani&quot;
* 1973 – &quot;Jagiellonia Białystok MKSB&quot;
* 1999 – &quot;Jagiellonia Białystok-Wersal Podlaski&quot;
* 2003 – &quot;Jagiellonia Białystok SSA&quot;

