* Chris Jackson – bass 
* Vinny Daraio – drums, percussion 
* Dustin Roth - drums, percussion 
* Andrew Elderbaum – bass, backing vocals 
* Jason Enz – drums, percussion 
* JR Manning – lead guitar 
* Jim Mitchell – drums, percussion 
* John &quot;Beatz&quot; Holohan – drums, percussion 

